  "formulaSource": "Service upgrade base pricing from HomeAdvisor and Angi 2025-2026 national average surveys for electrical service entrance upgrades. Material/labor split (35%/65%) based on NECA unit pricing guidelines. Meter relocation, underground conversion, and home age labor multipliers derived from NECA project complexity adjustments. Regional labor multipliers from Bureau of Labor Statistics Occupational Employment and Wage Statistics for electricians (SOC 47-2111). Permit costs from municipal electrical permit fee schedule surveys across 50 U.S. metro areas.",
